         <abstract id="aspace_3bcea00f84f2b9b7f976c4fef5544832">The papers consist of personal, business, and family letters written by members of the Wood family of Littleton, Middlesex, England. Correspondence between Thomas Wood and John Pack, in London, makes up the majority of the papers. There are also letters to Thomas Wood from his sons.</abstract>
